  "detailed_description": "The Halloween Decoration Sandbox is a creative open world game that lets users design their own home haunts. Pick from a wide selection of decorations to create the perfect experience which can be explored in VR as you collect candies by trick or treating.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438750/extras/1ebc33f2b040200294d4d10181841cdd.avif?t=1743087401\" width=500 height=162 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Modify terrain in an open world sandbox map editor.<br></li><li> Place scenery around the world.<br></li><li> Add Halloween decorations to the sandbox.<br></li><li> Walk around with your character trick or treating collecting candy throughout the sandbox.</li></ul><br><strong>Decorate Your Sandbox!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438750/extras/2185c3fe44572476e34ea03ca6d803bc.poster.avif?t=1743087401\" width=620 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438750/extras/2185c3fe44572476e34ea03ca6d803bc.webm?t=1743087401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438750/extras/2185c3fe44572476e34ea03ca6d803bc.mp4?t=1743087401\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Explore In Open World!</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438750/extras/0634a0db5a6f4b2192b330830d5f8672.poster.avif?t=1743087401\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1438750/extras/0634a0db5a6f4b2192b330830d5f8672.webm?t=1743087401\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.s